{ Issue 4 — type-resolution errors should surface in source order.
  Two cycle slots (A ↔ B on lines 9 and 12). Without the sort fix
  cycle errors come out in graph-traversal order; with the fix they
  come out in source order 9 → 12. }

BEGIN;

VARIABLE A;
A := B + 1;

VARIABLE B;
B := A * 2;

WRITE 6 A;
WRITE 6 B;

END;
